plot: MacKenzie Douthit is a 16 year old cheerleader from Miami, Oklahoma who is pregnant by her boyfriend, Josh McKee. On September 12, 2011, Douthit gives birth a baby boy, Gannon Dewayne McKee via C-section. The episode focuses on the hard decisions Douthit and McKee must both make as parents, with Douthit having to give up cheerleading and McKee being pressured to give up bull riding.—TatyanaR
